Hatch, 1950: 100. Type species: 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Stephens" baseAuthorityYear="1828" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="359" pageNumber="360" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chalceum">
